full_text:
No internet, got a good look going for my redo of the man eating unicorn painting, had an excellent day.

Guess I'll go to bed.
My son wants to start a Renaissance style outfit for cosplay and I have never been this excited to buy him clothes and accessories.

So we got excited the trailer park was going to bring in an actual dumpster trailer for our spring cleanup. Turns out they're only opening the regular mini car sized one for a week for 57 lots. It'll be full in a day. 
Face palm*
